# Audio fixtures are gitignored by default — they're often large and
# personal recordings. Sidecar .json files for HAND-CURATED fixtures
# ARE committed so the manifest of expected fixtures lives in version
# control.
#
# Synced fixtures (those pulled from production feedback via
# `pnpm bench:stt:sync`) are gitignored on BOTH the audio AND the
# sidecar, because the sidecar embeds user-dictated text that may
# contain PII. Force-commit individual ones with `git add -f` if you
# want them tracked.
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.flac
*.ogg
*.webm
*.aiff
feedback-*.json
